  <_summary>Organize and develop images from digital cameras</_summary>
  <translation type="gettext">darktable</translation>
  <description>
    <_p>
      darktable manages your digital negatives in a database and lets you
      view them through a lighttable. It also enables you to develop raw
      images and enhance them in a darkroom.
    </_p>
    <_p>
      Other modes besides lighttable and darkroom are a map for geotagging,
      tethering, print and a slideshow.
    </_p>
    <_p>
      darktable supports most modern camera's raw formats, and does all
      of its processing at very high precision.
    </_p>
  </description>
